\c 5
\s Rwiyo rwaDhebhora
\p
\v 1 Zvino Dhebhora naBharaki mwanakomana waAbhinowami vakaimba\x + Eki. 15.1. Map. 18.\x* nezuva iro vachiti:
\p
\v 2 Kudzai Jehovha, nekuda kwekutsiva kwetsivo paIsraeri\x + Det. 32.42. 2 Sam. 22.48. Map. 18.47.\x*, kana vanhu vakazvipa\x + 5.9. 2 Makor. 17.16.\x* nekuzvidira.
\v 3 Inzwai madzimambo, mupe nzeve \add imwi\add* machinda\x + Map. 2.2. Zvir. 31.4. Det. 32.1,3. Map. 2.10.\x*; ini, iyeni, ndichaimbira Jehovha; ndicharumbidza Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri nenziyo.
\v 4 Jehovha, pakubuda kwenyu paSeiri\x + Det. 33.2. Det. 4.11.\x*, pakutsika kwenyu muchibva musango reEdhomu\x + Map. 68.7.\x*, nyika yakadedera\x + Map. 68.8. 2 Sam. 22.8. Map. 18.7; 77.18. Nah. 1.5. Habh. 3.3,10.\x*, uye matenga akadonha, uye makore akadonha mvura.
\v 5 Makomo akayerera pamberi paJehovha\x + Isa. 64.1,3. Det. 4.11. Map. 97.5. Mik. 1.4.\x*, iro Sinai\x + Eki. 19.18.\x* pamberi paJehovha Mwari waIsraeri.
\v 6 Pamazuva aShamugari, mwanakomana waAnati\x + 3.31.\x*, pamazuva aJaeri\x + 4.17.\x*, nzira dzakapera\x + Rev. 26.22.\x*, nevafambi munzira vaifamba nenzira dzakakombama.
\v 7 Vagari vemaruwa vakapera\x + 5.11. Det. 3.5.\x* kwaIsraeri, vakapera, kusvika ini Dhebhora ndichisimuka, ndichisimuka, \add ini\add* mai kwaIsraeri.
\v 8 Vakasarudza vamwari vatsva\x + Det. 32.16. Vato. 2.12,17.\x*; ipapo kukava nehondo pamasuwo. Pakaonekwa here nhovo kana pfumo\x + 1 Sam. 13.19,22. Vato. 4.3.\x* pakati pezvuru makumi mana kwaIsraeri?
\v 9 Moyo wangu uri kuvapi vemurairo vekwaIsraeri, vanozvipa vachizvidira pakati pevanhu\x + 5.2.\x*; kudzai Jehovha!
\v 10 Vatasvi vemabhiza machena\x + Num.. 22.21. Vato. 10.4; 12.14. Zek. 9.9.\x*, vagari vemhasa dzinokosha\x + Map. 107.32. Isa. 28.6.\x*, nevafambi venzira, taurai.
\v 11 Painzwi revafuri veuta, pakati penzvimbo dzekuchera mvura\x + Gen.. 24.11.\x*, vacharondedzerapo mabasa akarurama aJehovha, mabasa akarurama emisha muIsraeri\x + 5.11. Det. 3.5.\x*. Ipapo vanhu vaJehovha vakaburukira kumasuwo.
\p
\v 12 Muka\x + Map. 57.8.\x*, muka, Dhebhora; muka, muka, taura rwiyo! Simuka Bharaki, utape vatapwa vako\x + Map. 68.18. VaEfe. 4.8.\x*, mwanakomana waAbhinowami.
\v 13 Ipapo wakaita musiiwa kuti atonge pamusoro pemadzimambo evanhu\x + Map. 49.14.\x*; Jehovha wakandiita nditonge pamusoro pevane simba.
\v 14 Kubva kuna Efuremu\x + 3.27.\x* mudzi wavo wairwisa Amareki\x + 3.13.\x*; shure kwako Bhenjamini, pakati pevanhu vako; kubva kuna Makiri\x + Num.. 32.39,40.\x* kwakaburuka vapi vemurairo\x + Det. 33.21.\x*, uye kubva kuna Zebhuruni avo vanokweva netsvimbo yemunyori.
\v 15 Uye machinda aIsasikari aiva naDhebhora, uye \add sa\add*Isasikari, wakadaro Bharaki\x + 4.14.\x*; akatumwa pamupata netsoka dzake. Pakuparadzana kwaRubheni mirangariro yemoyo yaiva mikuru.
\v 16 Wakagarirei pakati pematanga\x + Gen.. 49.14. Map. 68.13.\x*, kunzwa kuridza muridzo\x + Jer. 18.16.\x* kwemakwai\x + Num.. 32.1.\x*? Pakuparadzana kwaRubheni pane kunzvera kukuru kwemoyo.
\v 17 Giriyadhi wakagara mhiri kwaJoridhani\x + Josh. 13.24,25,26,27,28.\x*; naDhani wakagarirei pazvikepe\x + Josh. 19.46.\x*? Asheri wakasara pamahombekombe egungwa\x + Josh. 19.29,31.\x*, wakagara panopinda gungwa munyika.
\v 18 Zebhuruni\x + 4.10.\x* rudzi rwakazvidza mweya warwo kusvika parufu, naNafutari, pakakwirira pemunda.
\v 19 Madzimambo akauya akarwa; ipapo madzimambo eKenani akarwa paTaanaki\x + Josh. 12.21; 17.11. Vato. 1.27. 1 Madz. 4.12. Josh. 21.25.\x*, pamvura dzeMegidho\x + Josh. 12.21; 17.11. Vato. 1.27. 1 Madz. 4.12; 9.15. 2 Madz. 9.27; 23.29,30. 2 Makor. 35.22. Zek. 12.11. Zvak. 16.16.\x*; havana kutora zvakapambiwa zvesirivha\x + 4.15,16.\x*.
\v 20 Dziri kumatenga dzakarwa, nyeredzi dziri munzira yadzo dzakarwa naSisera.
\v 21 Rwizi Kishoni rwakavakukura\x + 4.7.\x*, irwo rwizi rwekare, rwizi Kishoni. Mweya wangu, iwe wakatsika-tsika simba.
\v 22 Ipapo akarovera pasi mahwanda emabhiza nekumhanya, kuri kumhanya kwevakasimba\x + Gen.. 49.24.\x* vavo.
\v 23 Tukai Merozi, anoreva mutumwa waJehovha, tukai zvinorwadza vagari varo; nokuti havana kuuya\x + 21.5,9,10. Neh. 3.5.\x* kurubatsiro rwaJehovha\x + 1 Sam. 18.17; 25.28.\x*, kurubatsiro rwaJehovha pavane simba.
\v 24 Ngaaropafadzwe kudarika vakadzi Jaeri, mukadzi waHebheri muKeni\x + 4.17.\x* ngaaropafadzwe kudarika vakadzi patende.
\v 25 Wakakumbira mvura\x + 4.19.\x*, \add iye\add* akamupa mukaka; wakamuvigira mukaka wakafa pandiro yeumambo.
\v 26 Wakatandavadza ruoko rwake pambambo\x + 4.21.\x*, neruoko rwerudyi rwake panyundo yemubati, akarova Sisera nenyundo, akaparadza musoro wake; wakabaya akaboora chavovo chake.
\v 27 Pakati nepakati petsoka dzake wakakotama, akawa, akarara; pakati nepakati petsoka dzake wakakotama, akawa; paakakotama ndipo paakawira aparara.
\v 28 Mai vaSisera vakadongorera nepahwindo\x + 2 Sam. 6.16.\x*, vakadanidzira nepautanda hwehwindo\x + Zvir. 7.6.\x*, \add ndokuti:\add* Ngoro yake inononokerei kusvika\x + Eki. 32.1.\x*? Sei achiverengera makumbo engoro dzake?
\v 29 Vakachenjera vevakadzi vake vanokudzwa vakamupindura, naiye wakadzosera mhinduro yake \add achiti\add*:
\v 30 Havana kuwana here vakagovana chakapambiwa\x + Eki. 15.9.\x*? Musikana \add kana\add* vasikana vaviri kumurume uyo neuyo; chakapambiwa chemavara-mavara kuna Sisera, chakapambiwa chemavara-mavara chakarukwa, mapandi maviri echemavara-mavara chakarukwa chemitsipa yemupambi?
\v 31 Saizvozvo ngavaparare vavengi venyu vose\x + Map. 83.9,10.\x*, Jehovha; asi ivo vanomuda \add ngavave\add* sekubuda kwezuva\x + 2 Sam. 23.4.\x* nesimba raro\x + Map. 19.4,5.\x*! Nyika ndokuzorora makore makumi mana\x + 3.11.\x*.